00:22:49,608 --> 00:22:52,648
for traumatic brain injury, no closer to
any cure

509
00:22:52,708 --> 00:22:54,968
for breast cancer, no closer to any cure

510
00:22:54,968 --> 00:22:56,288
for pancreatic cancer.

511
00:22:56,578 --> 00:22:59,168
We're no closer to any cure for most

512
00:22:59,188 --> 00:23:01,128
of the diseases that afflict us.

513
00:23:01,588 --> 00:23:04,008
In fact, for most human diseases out
