516
00:23:09,788 --> 00:23:13,248
So we are really behind, I would say -
farther behind

517
00:23:13,308 --> 00:23:17,008
than we should be at this point in
finding the treatments

518
00:23:17,028 --> 00:23:18,168
and the cures we need.

519
00:23:18,428 --> 00:23:21,368
Cancer is the second leading cause of
death in the USA.

520
00:23:22,188 --> 00:23:24,528
My grandmother, my aunt, my cousin,

521
00:23:24,748 --> 00:23:26,688
and several of my friend's parents have

522
00:23:26,688 --> 00:23:27,848
