527
00:23:36,668 --> 00:23:38,288
The people shaped holes in our lives.

528
00:23:39,808 --> 00:23:41,728
I don't know anyone who hasn't in some way

529
00:23:41,728 --> 00:23:42,808
been affected by cancer.

530
00:23:43,748 --> 00:23:46,368
The idea that we haven't been been
fighting these diseases

531
00:23:46,468 --> 00:23:49,968
as efficiently as possible is extremely
upsetting.

532
00:23:50,938 --> 00:23:53,208
Every time you have one of these medical

533
00:23:53,848 --> 00:23:57,008
