540
00:24:16,188 --> 00:24:17,488
We as scientists

541
00:24:17,828 --> 00:24:19,768
and as a society, need

542
00:24:19,768 --> 00:24:22,608
to think about the ethics of human hope.

543
00:24:22,908 --> 00:24:25,328
As long as they are continuing to put
money

544
00:24:25,838 --> 00:24:29,408
into methods like animal testing that
have been proven again

545
00:24:29,428 --> 00:24:33,208
and again, not to work, not to be
effective, not

546
00:24:33,208 --> 00:24:35,808
to be reliable, then they're really being

547
00:24:35,808 --> 00:24:37,248
disingenuous to the public.

548
00:24:37,598 --> 00:24:39,168
They need to come forward.

549
00:24:39,278 --> 00:24:41,448
They need to come clean about what
they're doing

550
00:24:41,748 --> 00:24:44,648
and how like animal testing is not
leading to treatments,

551
00:24:44,718 --> 00:24:46,008
despite of what they tell people.

552
00:24:46,228 --> 00:24:49,928
You are utilizing the vulnerability of
the human patients.

553
00:24:50,068 --> 00:24:51,088
You're getting their money

554
00:24:51,268 --> 00:24:52,808
and then you're not doing a good job

555
00:24:53,188 --> 00:24:54,768
and you're not getting anything in return

556
00:24:54,788 --> 00:24:56,688
for them. It's just not right.

557
00:24:57,138 --> 00:25:00,368
Oftentimes I think about all these
marathons

558
00:25:00,368 --> 00:25:03,648
that people have, and anytime I see
people running

559
00:25:03,708 --> 00:25:07,088
for the cure, I almost wanna go and stop
