1016
00:44:43,888 --> 00:44:47,328
The Animal Enterprise Terrorism Act is a
law designed to

1017
00:44:48,078 --> 00:44:50,408
protect animal using industries,

1018
00:44:50,558 --> 00:44:53,048
including the biomedical research
industry,

1019
00:44:53,268 --> 00:44:57,648
and to put enhanced criminal penalties on
anybody

1020
00:44:58,028 --> 00:45:02,368
