research facility

1021
00:45:02,388 --> 00:45:03,528
or other covered facility.

1022
00:45:03,628 --> 00:45:05,528
It was designed to be very broad

1023
00:45:05,868 --> 00:45:09,048
and to reach First Amendment activities
and

1024
00:45:09,068 --> 00:45:11,248
the Center for Constitutional Rights has
said that,

1025
00:45:11,248 --> 00:45:12,928
the ACLU has weighed in.

1026
00:45:13,038 --> 00:45:15,728
This was the result of legislative efforts

1027
00:45:15,908 --> 00:45:17,368
by industry interests

1028
00:45:17,668 --> 00:45:20,328
to basically criminalize their opponents.

1029
00:45:21,368 --> 00:45:23,288
Consider the case of "Stop Huntington
Animal

1030
00:45:23,288 --> 00:45:24,808
Cruelty," or SHAC.

1031
00:45:25,148 --> 00:45:26,568
To make a long story short,

1032
00:45:26,678 --> 00:45:29,888
