animals.

1036
00:45:37,348 --> 00:45:40,288
In response, a campaign, SHAC, was mounted

1037
00:45:40,288 --> 00:45:42,608
to get other businesses to divest from
HLS.

1038
00:45:43,228 --> 00:45:47,848
In 2004, Andy Stepanian, a SHAC activist,
was arrested

1039
00:45:47,848 --> 00:45:49,128
and charged with conspiring

1040
00:45:49,148 --> 00:45:51,768
to violate the law's precursor, the Animal

1041
00:45:51,768 --> 00:45:53,168
Enterprise Protection Act,

1042
00:45:53,278 --> 00:45:55,288
even though his activism was textbook

1043
00:45:55,288 --> 00:45:56,448
First Amendment activity.

1044
00:45:56,718 --> 00:45:58,768
They were arguing that we caused upwards

1045
00:45:58,768 --> 00:46:01,808
of $15 million worth of financial losses
