1046
00:46:01,808 --> 00:46:02,968
through our protest campaign.

1047
00:46:03,188 --> 00:46:04,408
We couldn't argue that part.

1048
00:46:05,008 --> 00:46:06,448
I couldn't argue the part that I didn't

1049
00:46:06,448 --> 00:46:07,488
travel across state lines.

1050
00:46:08,128 --> 00:46:10,008
I did. I couldn't argue the part

1051
00:46:10,008 --> 00:46:13,168
that I organized protests - I did. I
couldn't argue the part

1052
00:46:13,168 --> 00:46:14,968
that I "utilized facilities in foreign

1053
00:46:15,028 --> 00:46:17,968
and interstate commerce," in this case,
the internet.

1054
00:46:18,488 --> 00:46:20,888
I did. I did all of those things,

1055
00:46:21,308 --> 00:46:24,688
but all of those things were a
conglomerate

1056
00:46:24,748 --> 00:46:25,928
of legal activities.

1057
00:46:26,628 --> 00:46:27,888
And that collection

1058
00:46:27,888 --> 00:46:31,728
of legal activities somehow found me
guilty of

1059
00:46:32,248 --> 00:46:33,688
