1079
00:47:24,018 --> 00:47:25,738
I won't say that you will be criminalized

1080
00:47:25,738 --> 00:47:27,578
for making this film, but I'll say

1081
00:47:27,578 --> 00:47:30,208
that we are living in a moment in history

1082
00:47:30,338 --> 00:47:34,128
where it's becoming increasingly easy for
