1083
00:47:34,228 --> 00:47:36,048
to create designer statutes

1084
00:47:36,438 --> 00:47:38,088
that would criminalize this film.

1085
00:47:38,848 --> 00:47:40,488
A year earlier, I was depressed

1086
00:47:40,668 --> 00:47:42,568
and conflicted about taking meds for it.

1087
00:47:43,208 --> 00:47:45,528
I had no idea that making a documentary,

1088
00:47:45,528 --> 00:47:46,968
exploring my questions around

1089
00:47:46,968 --> 00:47:50,048
that could ever, in a million years,
violate an

1090
00:47:50,048 --> 00:47:51,128
anti-terrorism statute.

1091
00:47:51,808 --> 00:47:53,128
I knew this was a big industry

1092
00:47:53,228 --> 00:47:55,808
and that there would be pushback for
making a critical film,

1093
00:47:56,348 --> 00:47:57,408
but it really hit home

1094
00:47:57,408 --> 00:47:59,128
after talking to Andy Stepanian -

1095
00:47:59,578 --> 00:48:01,208
these forces put him in prison.

1096
00:48:02,028 --> 00:48:05,888
So I decided to call my co-producer,
