Let me make this very simple for you.

1129
00:49:23,798 --> 00:49:27,208
Virtually every single medical
convenience you can think of,

1130
00:49:27,338 --> 00:49:29,408
every medication you can take for
anything,

1131
00:49:29,708 --> 00:49:31,408
and there are thousands of medications
available

1132
00:49:31,508 --> 00:49:33,648
for all kinds of ailments, every vaccine,

1133
00:49:33,788 --> 00:49:37,688
so every preventive, every diagnostic,
you know, all

1134
00:49:37,688 --> 00:49:40,088
of these imaging techniques, every
surgical intervention,

1135
00:49:40,378 --> 00:49:43,728
every single medical convenience you can
think of that

1136
00:49:43,728 --> 00:49:45,568
has allowed us all to live 20,

1137
00:49:45,708 --> 00:49:48,128
or more, you know, 30 more years to have
this conversation

1138
00:49:49,108 --> 00:49:51,448
has started with research in animals.

1139
00:49:51,888 --> 00:49:53,848
I have personally witnessed animal studies

1140
00:49:54,278 --> 00:49:56,528
that resulted in new cancer therapies

1141
00:49:56,528 --> 00:49:57,848
that literally save lives.

1142
00:49:57,998 --> 00:49:59,128
When I was at Oregon Health

1143
