funerals.

1147
00:50:07,668 --> 00:50:09,168
And those patients are still alive

1148
00:50:09,258 --> 00:50:10,528
today thanks to that drug.

1149
00:50:10,638 --> 00:50:12,768
I've also witnessed an immunotherapy drug

1150
00:50:12,768 --> 00:50:14,648
that was created at an institution where
