1151
00:50:14,648 --> 00:50:16,088
to work. Another case

1152
00:50:16,138 --> 00:50:18,488
where people were literally planning
their funerals

1153
00:50:18,488 --> 00:50:19,488
and are alive today.

1154
00:50:19,908 --> 00:50:21,528
And those studies, once again, came

1155
00:50:21,528 --> 00:50:22,728
