It makes people think, well,

1164
00:50:40,018 --> 00:50:41,648
these things cure disease in animals

1165
00:50:41,648 --> 00:50:43,448
and they don't cure disease in people,
and

1166
00:50:43,588 --> 00:50:45,728
in many cases it has nothing to do with
