1167
00:50:45,918 --> 00:50:47,928
It's frequently used by animal rights
groups.

1168
00:50:48,388 --> 00:50:50,768
What's really interesting is actually if
you go back

1169
00:50:50,768 --> 00:50:54,728
and look at the NIH website, that website
