1170
00:50:54,988 --> 00:50:56,408
of animal studies whatsoever.

1171
00:50:56,588 --> 00:50:58,888
And the reason is because the process

1172
00:50:59,068 --> 00:51:00,288
of developing a new therapy

1173
00:51:00,388 --> 00:51:03,048
or a new medication involves a tremendous

1174
00:51:03,048 --> 00:51:04,248
