00:51:07,848 --> 00:51:09,168
that either is - gets through

1177
00:51:09,168 --> 00:51:10,808
the approval process or does not.

1178
00:51:11,508 --> 00:51:14,088
And that's approximately 5% right now.

1179
00:51:14,268 --> 00:51:16,768
And, and that's, that's essentially how
