1182
00:51:20,508 --> 00:51:22,088
and it's really unfortunate

1183
00:51:22,088 --> 00:51:23,848
that animal rights groups are claiming

1184
00:51:23,918 --> 00:51:25,328
that animals are the problem.

1185
00:51:25,668 --> 00:51:28,808
And so the use of this 95% figure is
actually

