1206
00:52:17,068 --> 00:52:18,728
to see if he could add some clarity.

1207
00:52:19,918 --> 00:52:23,248
Yeah, I mean, I've seen ranges from 70%

1208
00:52:23,668 --> 00:52:27,728
to 95% of drugs failing when they get to
