1220
00:52:51,928 --> 00:52:54,488
There are examples, like liver toxicity,

1221
00:52:54,578 --> 00:52:57,128
where we know the results in animals are

1222
00:52:57,128 --> 00:52:58,368
totally different than humans.

1223
00:52:58,548 --> 00:53:00,288
So the exact number is sort

1224
00:53:00,288 --> 00:53:03,768
of less important than the reality that
