1236
00:53:31,798 --> 00:53:34,288
From biomedical research to cheating at
monopoly

1237
00:53:34,288 --> 00:53:35,328
and gaslighting your cousins,

1238
00:53:36,038 --> 00:53:38,168
it's all too natural to feel like there's
