1245
00:53:53,948 --> 00:53:55,608
for understanding human health.

1246
00:53:55,948 --> 00:53:59,528
And I believe they were threatened by the
idea that up

1247
00:53:59,528 --> 00:54:00,808
and coming researchers

1248
00:54:00,988 --> 00:54:04,328
and doctors are really questioning not
the elephant in the

1249
00:54:04,328 --> 00:54:05,408
room, but the mouse in the room.

1250
00:54:05,788 --> 00:54:07,888
One of the, the most profound experiences

1251
00:54:07,958 --> 00:54:10,648
